  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK791">
<l>nāṭātu naṭṭaliṟ kēṭillai naṭṭapiṉ</l>
<l>vīṭillai naṭpāḷ pavarkku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As those who are of a friendly nature will not forsake (a friend) after once loving (him), there is no evil so great as contracting a friendship without due inquiry.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
